Bringing Holo Theme to Android 1.X and 2.X

How to install ?

# Git clone in Eclipse
# Be sure that the library option is checked in HoloEverywhere project and you added the library to your current work.
# Add: android:theme="@style/Theme.HoloEverywhereDark" in tour application manifest, you may also want to test Theme.HoloEverywhereLight...

